                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="value-card wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 style="color: #0d47a1 !important">Innovation</h3>
                    <p style="color:#212529 !important">We constantly seek better ways to deliver healthcare services.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="value-card wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 style="color: #0d47a1 !important">Integrity</h3>
                    <p style="color:#212529 !important">We uphold the highest ethical standards in all our practices.</p>
